centric approach chris also shares our passion for food and his highly relevant experience as a senior executive with publiclytraded food and beverage companies strongly positions him to lead advancepierre through its next phase of growth” in addition to sliva’s hiring the company announced several promotions including george chappelle who has been appointed coo he was previously senior vicepresident of supply chain and corporate development jim clough has been named chief commercial officer for the company he was most recently president of advancepierre’s foodservice business unit regarding simons’ transition hollis said “john has been instrumental in transforming advancepierre’s culture into one focused on collaboration and excellence and in building a worldclass management team under john’s leadership advancepierre has implemented the apf way our sustainable improvement program that transformed our business performance and enhanced our margin profile we look forward to continuing to benefit from john’s experience and guidance as chief executive officer throughout the transition period” before joining treehouse foods sliva spent six years as an executive at dean foods dallas previously he held various leadership roles and sales and marketing positions with eastman kodak co fort james corp and procter  gamble distributing co comment on this article we welcome your thoughtful comments please comply with our community rules your name name is required your email address email address is required add your comment the views expressed in the comments section of meat and poultry news do not reflect those of meat and poultry news or its parent company sosland publishing co kansas city mo concern regarding a specific comment may be registered with the editor by clicking the report abuse link enter code as it is shown required please enter code code does not match news global business trends regulatory food safety new technology bacon business product formulation archive mos