    et from treehouse foods inc oak brook ill july   prnewswire  treehouse foods inc nyse ths announced today a new alignment of its executive leadership with the hiring of christopher d sliva to the newlycreated position of chief operating officer of its bay valley foods operating unit and senior vice president of treehouse foods sliva  joins the company from dean foods where was chief commercial officer of fresh dairy directmorningstar  in his new role at treehouse sliva will work closely with bay valley food president harry j walsh and report directly to chairman president and chief executive officer sam k reed he will be based at corporate headquarters in oak brook illinois the rapid growth and increased complexity of our company requires a new alignment of our executive leadership reed said chris sliva is highly qualified for the coo role for the past six years he has been a key member of the executive leadership team of dean foods the parent from which treehouse foods was spun off in  prior to being named chief commercial officer for fresh dairy directmorningstar in  sliva was chief customer officer for deans white wave foods division and president and chief operating officer for the morningstar division his successful career in consumer packaged goods also includes positions at eastman kodak fort james corporation and procter  gamble  sliva holds a bachelors degree in business administration from washington university in st louis    about treehouse foods formed in  treehouse is a food manufacturer servicing primarily the retail grocery and foodservice channels its  major product lines include nondairy powdered creamer canned soup refrigerated and shelf stable salad dressings dips and sauces powdered drink mixes instant oatmeal and hot cereals macaroni and cheese skillet dinners and other valueadded side dishes and salads salsa and mexican sauces jams and pie fillings under the ed smith brand name pickles and related products and other food products including aseptic sauces and liquid nondairy creamer treehouse believes it is the largest manufacturer of pickles and nondairy powdered creamer in the united states and the largest manufacturer of private label salad dressings powdered drink mixes and instant hot cereals in the united states and canada based on sales volume  treehouses annual sales are in excess of  billion the company has  manufacturing plants and more than  employees contact ron bottrell hillknowlton strategies phone  email ronbottrellhkstrategiescom source treehouse foods inc view table fullscreen view table fullscreen journalists and bloggers the news you need when you need it join pr newswire for journalists to access all of the free services designated to make your job easier in need of subject matter experts for your story submit a free profnet request and find the sources you need learn more aug 0  0 et preview treehouse foods inc reports second quarter  results jun    et preview treehouse foods inc to present at the  william blair growth stock conference my news release contains wide tables view fullscreen read more jun   0 et treehouse foods inc names lee j wise as vice president jun   0 et treehouse foods inc announces the appointment of robert b jun   0 et treehouse foods announces webcast of second quarter  earnings looking to send a news release with pr newswire take advantage of the worlds leading distribution platform sign up to get started request more information have an account log in search searching for your content advanced search